{
  "texts": [
    "This scale allowed participants to express their level of agreement with statements related to their experience using ChatGPT.",
    "The reliability of the instrument was verified using a Cronbach's alpha, ensuring internal consistency, and its validity was confirmed through content validation conducted by a panel of experts, ensuring that the evaluated dimensions accurately reflect the relevant constructs in the context of the study.A validated rubric was used to evaluate investigative competencies across six criteria: coherence, precision, originality, content depth, problem-solving ability, and source utilization.",
    "The content validity index of the instrument was confirmed by a panel of experts in educational research, obtaining a validity index of 0.85, indicating high validity.",
    "The reliability of the instrument was measured using Cronbach's alpha coefficient, yielding a value of 0.88, which reflects excellent internal consistency.",
    "E. Description of Rubric LevelsVery Good: The work meets or exceeds all expectations in the evaluated criterion."
  ]
}